						"XMPPChatActivity#send.onclicklistener Sending text "
								+ text + " to " + to);
				Message msg = new Message("push", Message.Type.chat);
				msg.setBody(text);
				if (xmppManager == null) {
					Log.i(LOGTAG,
							"XMPPChatActivity#send.onclicklistener xmppmanager is null");
					return;
